metadata.name: Song Of Ukraine #1
metadata.description:
«Giant song of Ukraine» is a visual collection of images made by AI from photos from the "Giant" series and the words of the Anthem of Ukraine.
We have an opportunity to see how artificial intelligence perceives the longing and desire for freedom from the words of the anthem and interprets the images.
The National Anthem of Ukraine is one of the main state symbols of Ukraine along with the flag and coat of arms. The national anthem is the song "Ukraine's Glory and Freedom have not yet died".
